# Docs, copy, and deliverables

- For README, architecture notes, deployment docs, API docs: use writer (and document-specialist when external references are needed).
- For editorial consistency and polish: use Every style editor skills when appropriate.
- If the deliverable is a PDF (generate/extract/verify layout): use pdf skill.
